@startuml readme-core-model-overview
'==============================================================================
' Diagram  : Core Model Overview (README companion)
' Version  : v2
' Date     : 2026-06-17
' Audience : README / docs readers — the main domain concepts only.
' Type     : SIMPLIFIED MAINTAINED COMPANION of core-type-hierarchy.puml.
'            One idea: a workflow controls the AI — it contains steps, steps use
'            behaviours, and only agent behaviours invoke an agent.
' Source   : agentforge4j-core (live source) + core-type-hierarchy.puml.
'==============================================================================
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
hide empty members
top to bottom direction

class Workflow
class Step
class Behaviour
class Agent
class Transition

Workflow "1" *-- "*" Step : contains
Step --> Behaviour : uses
Behaviour ..> Agent : may invoke
Step --> Transition : gated by

@enduml
